# 🔹 3) Tempo Médio de Escape (Lei de Kramers)

```python
def mean_escape_time(xi, T):
    traj = simulate_1d(xi, T)
    signs = np.sign(traj)
    changes = np.where(np.diff(signs) != 0)[0]

    if len(changes) < 2:
        return np.nan

    intervals = np.diff(changes)
    return np.mean(intervals) * dt

